sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / KFP Pipeline
    participant Exp as AI4RAGExperiment
    participant MPS as ModelsPreSelector
    participant GAM as GAMOptimizer
    participant Chunker as LangChainChunker
    participant EmbModel as OGXEmbeddingModel
    participant VS as OGXVectorStore
    participant FM as OGXFoundationModel
    participant OGX as OGX Server<br/>HTTPS + TLS<br/>API Key Auth
    participant Chroma as ChromaDB<br/>(In-Memory)
    participant Eval as UnitxtEvaluator
    participant Handler as EventHandler

    Note over User,Handler: Flow 1: RAG Optimization Experiment

    User->>Exp: Start optimization<br/>(documents, benchmarks, search_space)

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Exp,Chroma: Phase 1: Models Pre-Selection (if >3 FMs or >2 EMs)
        Exp->>MPS: Pre-select top models
        MPS->>OGX: POST /embeddings (embed sample docs)<br/>HTTPS/TLS, API Key
        OGX-->>MPS: Embedding vectors
        MPS->>Chroma: Store embeddings (in-memory)
        Chroma-->>MPS: Stored
        MPS->>Chroma: Query similar chunks
        Chroma-->>MPS: Retrieved chunks
        MPS->>OGX: POST /chat/completions (generate answers)<br/>HTTPS/TLS, API Key
        OGX-->>MPS: Generated answers
        MPS->>Eval: Evaluate (faithfulness, correctness)
        Eval-->>MPS: Metric scores
        MPS-->>Exp: Top-N models selected
    end

    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Note over Exp,Handler: Phase 2: GAM Optimization Loop
        Exp->>GAM: Initialize optimizer with search space
        loop For each iteration
            GAM->>GAM: Predict promising params (LinearGAM)
            GAM->>Exp: Next parameter combination

            Note over Exp,Eval: Single RAG Evaluation
            Exp->>Chunker: Chunk documents<br/>(RecursiveCharacterTextSplitter)
            Chunker-->>Exp: Document chunks

            Exp->>EmbModel: Embed chunks
            EmbModel->>OGX: POST /embeddings<br/>HTTPS/TLS, API Key
            OGX-->>EmbModel: Embedding vectors

            Exp->>VS: Create vector store & insert chunks
            VS->>OGX: POST /vector_stores + POST /vector_io/insert<br/>HTTPS/TLS, API Key
            OGX-->>VS: Stored

            loop For each benchmark question (ThreadPoolExecutor, max 10)
                Exp->>VS: Query similar chunks
                VS->>OGX: POST /vector_io/query<br/>HTTPS/TLS, API Key
                OGX-->>VS: Retrieved chunks
                Exp->>FM: Generate answer with context
                FM->>OGX: POST /chat/completions<br/>HTTPS/TLS, API Key
                OGX-->>FM: Generated answer
            end

            Exp->>Eval: Evaluate all answers
            Eval-->>Exp: Metric scores

            Exp->>GAM: Record score for params
            GAM->>GAM: Update GAM model

            Exp->>Handler: Emit iteration results
            Handler-->>User: Progress update
        end
    end

    Exp->>Handler: Emit final results
    Handler-->>User: Best RAG configuration + scores
